name: FA2.py Demo
description:
This is a didactic reference implementation of FA2, a.k.a. TZIP-012, using SmartPy.

This particular contract uses the configuration named: FA2-mutez.

It is “The default with mutez transfer entry-point.”

This instance is meant to show/test various
features of https://tzcomet.io, with a few more or less valid tokens …

Feel free to report issues at https://github.com/tqtezos/TZComet/issues.
